gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 117, Knicks 108
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Knicks, 117-108. Franz Wagner recorded a season-high 32 points, along with nine rebounds and four steals for the Magic, while Paolo Banchero added 29 points, 10 rebounds, and four assists in the victory. Julius Randle (38 points, 12 rebounds, six assists) and Jalen Brunson (20 points, seven rebounds, eight assists) combined for 58 points for the Knicks in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 19-12 on the season, while the Knicks fall to 17-14.
